OpenAI response for Prompt: Jarvis tell me about India 
 *************************



India is a country located in South Asia. It is the seventh-largest country in the world by area and the second-most populous country with over 1.3 billion people. It is bordered by Bangladesh, Pakistan, China, Nepal, Bhutan, Burma and Afghanistan. India is a large and diverse country with a variety of landscapes, climates, and cultures. It is home to the Indus Valley Civilization, one of the world’s oldest, and is a land of deep religious and cultural diversity. India is also home to some of the world’s most important languages, including Hindi and English. The country is also known for its rich history, vibrant culture, and cuisines.